DESCRIPTION :
The To-Do app is a simple yet efficient task management application designed to help users organize and prioritize their daily tasks. 
It allows users to add, edit, and delete tasks, set due dates, and mark tasks as completed. 
This app is built with the goal of increasing productivity and keeping track of personal or work-related responsibilities.

KEY FEATURES :
Add new tasks with task names.
Edit and update existing tasks. 
Delete individual tasks or clear all. 
Mark tasks as completed/incomplete.

What I Learned :
DOM manipulation and event handling. 
Basics of CRUD operations. 
Managing application state. 
Storing and retrieving data using LocalStorage. 
Writing clean and maintainable code. 
UI/UX design principles.
